# scaffold-agent workspace

- This package **generates** monorepos; consumer apps are **not** this folder.
- After editing **`src/**/*.ts`**, run **`npm run build`** before validating **`dist/cli.js`**.
- Project-wide agent instructions: **`AGENTS.md`**. Claude Code: **`CLAUDE.md`** imports it.
- Prefer minimal diffs in **`src/actions/scaffold.ts`** (large embedded templates).
- Do not commit secrets; **`ONECLAW_AGENT_ID`** is a UUID, not an Ethereum address.
